<plot>El Trip is an adventurous journey between four friends who live in Mexicali B.C. and travel across the border to see the premiere of the movie, "The Doors". They stop at their local drug dealer's house for party favors to enhance their viewing pleasure. Much to their surprise, they arrive a week early for the premiere date and decide to return to Mexico. Before they make it across the border, they are caught smoking weed in Fernando's VW Bus and try to outwit the police officers to avoid getting arrested. They succeed to cross the border in a state of panic and are forced to deal with the consequences of their actions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?174199</url></doc>
